  "description": "<h3><strong>Marine Service Engineer</strong></h3><p><strong>Office location : Boon Lay </strong></p><p><strong>Working Location: On board ship</strong></p><p><strong>Working days : 5 days (Mon- Friday)</strong></p><p><strong>Working hours : 8am - 5pm</strong></p><p><strong>Salary : $2,000-$2,800 basic + OT + Allowances (Gross Salary $3,000 - $4,000)</strong></p><p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct periodic inspections, repair, service and maintenance of marine equipment to ensure reliable<br />operation.</li><li>Collaborate with clients and superintendents to deliver quality services efficiently.</li><li>Generate reports and present findings to relevant personnel.</li><li>Provide remote troubleshooting support through emails, ensuring customer issues are resolved promptly to maintain high satisfaction levels.<br /><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong></li><li>Diploma in Engineering or equivalent (Electrical/Electronics/Mechanical/Mechatronics).</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>📲Interested candidates, please WhatsApp your resume to: +65 9642 0989 (Han) 📧 Or email your resume to: </strong><a href=\"https://employer.mycareersfuture.gov.sg/jobs/6723-senior-hr-executive-education-sector-marine-parade-35k%E2%80%934k-hr-lifecycle-er-supreme-hr-advisory-f4d18bea51dfbe07dff1bccc5ef1e127/view#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">supreme.cc.han@gmail.com</a><strong></strong></p><p><strong>👤Chaw Chiaw Han | R22106723🏢 The Supreme HR Advisory Pte Ltd | EA 14C7279</strong></p>",
